      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "まだだいぶあるのに、早いわね、優",
      "startTime": 10.2286300659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなにテレビに食いついて、何を観てるの？",
      "startTime": 13.5689795494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……私の声、聞こえてる？",
      "startTime": 18.6356462161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……おーい、優ちゃーん。反応がない……。あれ？",
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが観てるのって、アニメ？　これって……",
      "startTime": 28.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確か『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』っていうアニメよね",
      "startTime": 34.2796373685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "名前だけなら知ってるわ。私が小さい頃からあったもの",
      "startTime": 38.1350865001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うわ～懐かしい～！　小学校低学年くらいまで観てたよ",
      "startTime": 42.6463040352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "ごっこ遊び、お兄ちゃんに付き合ってもらったな～",
      "startTime": 48.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ……このエンディングテーマソング、素敵ね",
      "startTime": 52.3044222832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "聞き心地のいいメロディーと、発声……",
      "startTime": 56.9377556165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "口ずさみたくなるようなキャッチーなフレーズ",
      "startTime": 60.1044222832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "メッセージ性の高い歌詞……どれも良く出来てる",
      "startTime": 63.4377556165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "さっすが瑠依ちゃん！！！",
      "startTime": 68.1377556165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "きゃっ！",
      "startTime": 70.3044222832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "曲の良さに気付けるんは、瑠依ちゃんの耳がええからや",
      "startTime": 71.5038555503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "でもこの作品の良さはそれだけやない",
      "startTime": 74.9371888836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大人の鑑賞にも耐えうるストーリーと演出",
      "startTime": 77.7705201824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "作り込まれたキャラクター、どれをとっても一級品",
      "startTime": 80.7257987493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただの女児向けアニメやと舐めたらいけません",
      "startTime": 84.4705176393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちも、小さい頃はただ好きで観てただけなんやけど",
      "startTime": 87.2371863405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "成長するにつれて、セリフの深みも分かってきて",
      "startTime": 91.0038489381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今やうちの人生の教科書と言っても過言ではない",
      "startTime": 94.3705176393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ゆ、優ちゃん、凄い早口！",
      "startTime": 98.3705156047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "も～、気付いてたならもっと早く言ってよ～",
      "startTime": 102.066662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あはは、ごめんなぁ。ええところやったから",
      "startTime": 106.0521028239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "つい見入ってしまってん。はぁ、今週もええ話やったわ",
      "startTime": 109.9854381918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おでんによって深まったメイン戦士三人の絆……",
      "startTime": 116.0521002808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……尊い……夕飯はおでんにしましょ……",
      "startTime": 120.4224570895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "優がそこまで評価するのだから、素晴らしい作品なのね",
      "startTime": 125.5187669474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "子供の頃、ちゃんと観ておけば良かったわ……",
      "startTime": 131.3521023153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今からでも遅ないよ。毎週録画しとるし、過去作も",
