      "text": "劇場版も円盤で持っとるから、良かったら一緒に観よ？",
      "startTime": 139.2865817173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "全部！？　さすが優ちゃん、ファンの鑑だね！",
      "startTime": 144.2187669474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、今度私にも貸してもらえるかなぁ？",
      "startTime": 149.766662089,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4400.004577700002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
